<h2 class="section-title"><%= @labels['about'] %></h2>
<p itemprop="description">As a lead-up to <a href="http://reinventpayphones.splashthat.com" target="_blank"> NYC's Reinvent Payphone Design Challenge </a>, we are hosting Payphone Hack Day to build physical or virtual payphone prototypes. Designers, engineers, students -- bring yourself, your gear and your team, or form a team at the hack day itself.</p>

<p>The <a href="http://www.nyc.gov/html/digital/html/rules/reinvent_payphones.html" target="_blank">rules</a> that apply to the City's Reinvent Payphones Design Challenge also apply here.</p>
